"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-paris-olympics-3x3-basketball-tv-schedule-full-list-times-channels-live\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"All eyes in the sporting world this summer will be on France for the upcoming 2024 Olympics in Paris.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 54, \"end\": 60, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.988646318721282, \"rank\": 0.01080478376432695, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 95, \"end\": 100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997316991, \"rank\": 2.682956484445446e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While men's and women's teams from around the globe will battle for the traditional gold medal in team basketball, hoopers around the world will also be competing for a spot on the podium in 3x3 basketball for the second time in the history of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 103, \"to\": 360, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Like all Olympic sports, the television schedule\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094with both live and delayed broadcasts\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094can be difficult to track.\", \"from\": 362, \"to\": 479, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Here's everything you need to know about 3x3 Olympic basketball this summer.\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 556, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If you are interested in checking out the five-on-five Olympic basketball schedule,follow this link.\", \"from\": 558, \"to\": 658, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"3x3 basketball was featured at several youth Olympic games over the years, but it wasn't until 2021 when it made its debut at the Tokyo Olympics.\", \"from\": 660, \"to\": 805, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Latvia's 3x3 men's basketball team won gold in Tokyo, defeating the Russian Olympic Committee in the final.\", \"from\": 807, \"to\": 914, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 807, \"end\": 813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\", \"score\": 0.9944741343391004, \"rank\": 0.004502006750498806, \"text\": \"Latvia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Latvia\"}, {\"begin\": 854, \"end\": 859, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.9999660585457107, \"rank\": 3.394143636850455e-05, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}, {\"begin\": 875, \"end\": 900, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"score\": 0.999395293401291, \"rank\": 0.00040665427566213656, \"text\": \"Russian Olympic Committee\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia_men's_national_ice_hockey_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Serbia earned the bronze medal.\", \"from\": 915, \"to\": 946, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 915, \"end\": 921, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9957205489052603, \"rank\": 0.004275347399829288, \"text\": \"Serbia\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Serbia_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the women's side, Team USA\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094led by Kelsey Plum, Jackie Young, Allisha Gray and Stefanie Dolson\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094won the gold medal, beating out the ROC (silver) and China (bron