ank\": 1.9268989813259435e-06, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/USA_Network\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"and CNBC\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094there will be tape-delayed coverage of the tournament throughout the Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 6953, \"to\": 7047, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Encore coverage of the 3x3 basketball tournament will be offered throughout the Olympics on NBC, USA Network and E!.\", \"from\": 7049, \"to\": 7165, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7141, \"end\": 7144, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"score\": 0.9999714679461729, \"rank\": 2.8352516426780648e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 7146, \"end\": 7157, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"score\": 0.9997220101714397, \"rank\": 0.0002780671285957245, \"text\": \"USA Network\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBCSN\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"TheNBCUniversal networksthat will be broadcasting the Olympic Games in Paris are available on most cable packages.\", \"from\": 7167, \"to\": 7281, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7238, \"end\": 7243, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997316991, \"rank\": 2.682956484445446e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ensure your cable package has access to these networks before the opening ceremony on July 26.\", \"from\": 7282, \"to\": 7376, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every 3x3 basketball game will be streamed live on Peacock, NBC's exclusive streaming service.\", \"from\": 7378, \"to\"